message.entry: Expand subsystem cannot be applied to Model blocks.
Expand subsystem can only be applied to Subsystem blocks.
Expand subsystem cannot be applied to Atomic Subsystem blocks.
Expand subsystem cannot be applied to Enabled Subsystem blocks.
Expand subsystem cannot be applied to Triggered Subsystem blocks.
Expand subsystem cannot be applied to Enabled and Triggered Subsystem blocks.
Expand subsystem cannot be applied to Function Call Subsystem blocks.
Expand subsystem cannot be applied to If Action Subsystem blocks.
Expand subsystem cannot be applied to Iterator Subsystem blocks.
Expand subsystem cannot be applied to Variant Subsystem blocks.
Expand subsystem cannot be applied to Configurable Subsystem blocks.
Expand subsystem cannot be applied to subsystems set to ReadOnly or NoReadOrWrite.
Expand subsystem cannot be applied to subsystems that own harnesses.
Expand subsystem cannot be applied to subsystems that own observers.
Expand subsystem cannot be applied to masked subsystems with hidden contents.
Expand subsystem cannot be applied to masked subsystems.
Expand subsystem can not be applied to masked subsystems. You can remove the mask. (You cannot undo this operation.)
Expand subsystem cannot be applied to library links.
Expand subsystem can not be applied to library links. You can disable the link. (You cannot undo this operation.)
Expand subsystem cannot be applied to commented subsystems.
Expand subsystem can not be applied to commented subsystems. You can uncomment the block. (You cannot undo this operation.)
Expand subsystem cannot be applied to blocks with linked requirements.You can delete the subsystem requirements. (You cannot undo this operation.)
Expand subsystem cannot be applied to blocks with internally linked requirements. You can move the requirements to an external file. (You cannot undo this operation.)
Expand subsystem can not be applied to blocks with simulation callbacks (InitFcn, StartFcn, ContinueFcn, PauseFcn, and StopFcn)
Expand subsystem cannot be applied inside Variant Subsystem blocks.
Expand subsystem cannot be applied to subsystems with composite ports.
